EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO EDUCATION -- CURRICULUM
***
1 This act would require every high school to offer a yearlong “ethnic studies” course
2 studying Rhode Island and American history and the experiences of racialized communities in
3 Rhode Island and the United States. This act would also direct the establishment of an ethnic studies
4 leadership council to oversee implementation of the requirements of this section.
5 This act would take effect on July 1, 2025.
